title: Lenore The Cute Little Dead Girl V2 #8
description:
Lenore The Cute Little Dead Girl V2 #8

A beloved Lenore character must die -- forever!!!
Thats right: one of your beloved undead is going to reach the end of their improbably animated rope ... and be removed from the afterlife for all eternity! Meanwhile, Lenore terrorises a ghost hunting TV show -- and the origin of Taxidermy is finally revealed!
